content.title: Cosmetic Surgeons PAI
paragraphs: Our cosmetic surgeons at Preecha Aesthetic Institute constitutes 6 of the most qualified plastic surgeons in the country are the most experienced board certified cosmetic surgeons in their specialized fields.Most have held professorship teaching posts at the most prestigious medical schools in Thailand.  Owing to this, our patients benefit greatly from various medical school research teams.

In order to ensure patients’ satisfaction and safety, we have at least one surgeon for each discipline ranging from general plastic, cosmetic surgery, Head and Neck Microsurgery, Hand surgery and Maxillofacial surgery, which enables the PAI to offer its patients superior care.

Dr Preecha Tiewtranon is the head of PAI and the leader in modern Plastic and Reconstructive and Aesthetic Surgery, the former Associate Professor Chairman of the Cosmetic Surgery Unit of the medical school of King Chulalongkorn University, President of Plastic and Reconstructive Surgeons of Thailand and President of the Society of Aesthetic Surgeons of Thailand.Dr. Preecha started performing SRS or GRS procedures in 1978 and most of the qualified SRS surgeons in Thailand were trained by him.  By the year 2005, Dr. Preecha had personally performed over 30,000 cosmetic and plastic surgeries and over 3,500 SRS and facial feminization surgeries.

Preecha Aesthetic Institute is the first multidisciplinary aesthetic surgery institute. PAI offers a complete range of options for plastic and cosmetic surgery in up to date hospital facilities with highly qualified cosmetic surgeons who are registered with the Diplomat American Board of Surgery, Certified Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery (USA, Australia, Thailand).Education Background:M.D. Chulalongkorn University, Bangkok, Thailand.– 1967-68 Surgery Resident, New York Hospital, N.Y., USA.– 1968-70 Surgery Resident, Providence Hospital, Southfield, Michigan.– 1970-73 Surgery Resident, Roswell Park Memorial Institute, Buffalo,N.Y., USA.– 1973 Fellow Surgical Oncology, Roswell Park Memorial InstituteBuffalo, N.Y., USA.– 1975 Cosmetic Surgery, Albany Cosmetic Surgery, Albany, N.
